				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Druids hold court to determine whether or not to lock up a tiefling child for stealing their precious artifact. If you fail to stop them, the child tries to run and is attacked by their guardian snakes.\r\n\r\nSagha the druid leader is the main player in this scene. She is machiavellian, and flips to evil should the snakes attack the child."
				}
			}
